    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA240-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">1. itu piriviṭai melinta talaimakaḷ colliyatu.
            2. neñciṉāl poruḷ valikkappaṭṭu āṟṟāṉāya talaimakaṉ colliyatūumām.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">1. This what SHE said who has become weak in the time of separation. 2. It is also when HE said, being unable to bear it as he was being compelled by [his] heart to [earn] wealth.</p>
        </div>
      <div xml:id="NA240">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            aitē kammaviv vulakupaṭait tōṉē</l>
<l>            vaiyēr vāleyiṟ ṟoṇṇutaṟ kuṟumakaḷ</l>
<l>            kaikavar muyakka meyyuṟat tiruki</l>
<l>            yēṅkuyirp paṭṭa vīṅkumulai yākan</l>
<l>            tuyiliṭaip paṭūun taṉmaiya tāyiṉum </l>
<l>            veyilvey tuṟṟa paralava lotukkiṟ</l>
<l>            kaṇicciyiṟ kuḻitta kūva ṉaṇṇi</l>
<l>            yāṉvaḻip paṭunar tōṇṭiya pattal</l>
<l>            yāṉai yiṉanirai vauvum</l>
<l>            kāṉan tiṇṇiya malaipōṉ ṟiciṉē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Let him go easily, him who created this world.</l>
<l rend="indent2">Even if it is so that sleep comes at intervalls,</l>
<l>the bosom with swelling breasts that sighed lamentingly</l>
<l rend="indent">of the little woman with bright forehead [and] sharp upright pure teeth,</l>
<l rend="indent2">wrung [by desire] for [his] embrace to take place, seized by [his] hands,</l>
<l>– it is like the firm forest mountains,</l>
<l rend="indent">where the row of a group of elephants snatches</l>
<l rend="indent2">the hollowed bucket of those that are on the way to the cows,</l>
<l rend="indent3">situated at the well hollowed out by the goad</l>
<l rend="indent4">in a separate spot of the pebbly depression hot in the sunlight.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
